{
  "stem": "26142.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the local people, they were two years under the Russian rule, and what they were missing mostly was clothing, and so they would sell something if you had-- well, we took along some underwear and some other clothing.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So if you sold some underwear you were able to get either milk, or eggs, or bread, or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So how do I know it was Shabbos?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That it was already a week?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We asked the people in that barn, the mayor's son, if there are Jewish people here at this village.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, yes, there is one Jewish family, and he is down there by the well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, a local community, they had a well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, I picked up with my brother, Tsvi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Moishe and the children, they stayed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And meantime, my sister-in-law, Manci, was able to barter for some underwear or whatever she had, and got a little milk for the children and something to eat.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Tsvi and I took off in the direction that he showed where-- so we came to a place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We saw the local well where the people bring their water, and we got into a house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We saw, of course, when I looked at the house I saw that there is a mezuzah, so I knew that we are in the right place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We found a man slumped over a chair by the table, and he was kind of-- it was a hot day, and he was kind of taking a nap.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came in we woke him up, and then I saw that there was a white tablecloth on the table.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I realized it was Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I saw a few crumbs, and millions and millions of flies were on that table.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
